r>2. 规划手里重要但不紧急的任务-&gt; 额度富裕 -&gt; 直接开蹬<br>3. 手里紧急的任务 -&gt; 古法编程 or 便宜模型</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17890612\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/22bf38ab308d4f128fdc6c9b1759a0c4?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"xhfx\" data-uid=\"510153\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>4</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/xhfx\">xhfx</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 09:28:37 +08:00\">23h 10m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>重置次数都要到期了..</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17890635\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b349/a1af/415096_normal.png?m=1618586856\" alt=\"lujiaosama\" data-uid=\"415096\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>5</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/lujiaosama\">lujiaosama</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 09:31:05 +08:00\">23h 8m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>5.6 是不是有什么技术可以优化输入输出，导致猛猛发额度</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17890738\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3ae3/1324/171697_normal.png?m=1703596600\" alt=\"geese1028\" data-uid=\"171697\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>11</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/geese1028\">geese1028</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 09:43:13 +08:00\">22h 56m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <div><p>要不是 fiat24 挂了，我早就升级 pro 了</p><p>确实爽，GLM 只配干点脏活累活，一点脑子都不能动。</p></div>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17890740\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d1de2846679e39dcd5a05c49fc5eb2f2?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"Rliey\" data-uid=\"613404\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>12</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/Rliey\">Rliey</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 09:43:19 +08:00\">22h 56m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>天天重置 我蹬不过来，昨天还想蹬完今天用重置卡，不然重置卡 27 就到期了，又重置了</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17890753\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3edbc3b933443b5246a007f1e55b2821?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"jioswu\" data-uid=\"207044\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>13</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/jioswu\">jioswu</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 09:45:13 +08:00\">22h 54m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>昨天刚重置,亏大发了</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17890823\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/befd/b8a6/462863_normal.png?m=1766557690\" alt=\"DICK23\" data-uid=\"462863\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>14</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/DICK23\">DICK23</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 09:57:07 +08:00\">22h 42m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>昨天几个任务蹬到 70%了，今天又给重置了，好几个 reset 都快过期了</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17890874\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b4b3448fdb9c5cc4ea62babbd10b45f6?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"jerseyhero\" data-uid=\"81419\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>16</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/jerseyhero\">jerseyhero</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 10:07:37 +08:00\">22h 31m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>但是我昨天还有 4 张卡，今天剩 3 张卡了，我都是数着卡过日子的，消失的卡 25 号过期，气死我了</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17890913\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/bce0d70ce0b620a82631ba0335067bec?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"Tsea\" data-uid=\"821686\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>17</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/Tsea\">Tsea</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 10:14:13 +08:00\">22h 25m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>我的 pro 过期了还能用</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17890922\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4676b54daa0f44b885474248e64b6972?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"ntdll\" data-uid=\"148771\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>18</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/ntdll\">ntdll</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 10:16:39 +08:00\">22h 22m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <div><p>最近这半个月确实总重置，用量也比以前豪放了很多，统计了一下，半个月用了 6000 多刀的额度。而且由于重置次数频繁，导致之前送的重置机会都没地方用。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/KVbUC4M.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KVbUC4M.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a></p></div>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17891046\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4852/774b/519159_normal.png?m=1739529533\" alt=\"kfitfk\" data-uid=\"519159\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>19</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/kfitfk\">kfitfk</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 10:37:31 +08:00\">22h 1m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>昨天刚好用到剩 3%，到点下班，就等着他重置。早上过来发现确实 100% 了</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17891063\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3bcc/4623/369913_normal.png?m=1666949302\" alt=\"N1ckl32\" data-uid=\"369913\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>20</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/N1ckl32\">N1ckl32</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 10:40:55 +08:00\">21h 58m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>昨天刚把 3 次重置机会用完，今天就又重置了，太及时了 =.=</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17891079\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1821/014d/458384_normal.png?m=1715408573\" alt=\"wzzexe\" data-uid=\"458384\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>21</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/wzzexe\">wzzexe</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 10:42:57 +08:00\">21h 56m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>感觉 5.6 的额度消耗非常快，200 刀的额度一天就用完了。之前有 5 小时限制的时候没有那么快，这难道不是是他们让你消费的手段吗？</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17891300\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3da6/bca1/579014_normal.png?m=1655454180\" alt=\"xubeiyou\" data-uid=\"579014\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>23</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/xubeiyou\">xubeiyou</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 11:12:46 +08:00\">21h 26m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>我最近半个月用了三次重置机会了 还剩下最后的一次 一个月到期 昨天就只是剩下 20 了  哎 还好重置了 但是有时候给人一种准备要饭的感觉  我次奥  这 5xpro 额度真不耐用了</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17891369\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3b50e8cb3bae4d273a6e6b07f46cab6b?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"biubiula\" data-uid=\"311234\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>25</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/biubiula\">biubiula</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 11:22:21 +08:00\">21h 16m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>好气，昨天下午蹬完犹豫要不要用重置卡就要过期了，等到晚上用了，今天一看又重置了</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17891397\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7b4e/82cb/32439_normal.png?m=1783061135\" alt=\"inyfee\" data-uid=\"32439\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>26</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/inyfee\">inyfee</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 11:25:03 +08:00\">21h 14m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <div><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/izT4Fuq.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/izT4Fuq.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a></p><p>搞得我现在马上给我的工具写个额度提示上去，方便我快速看到变化。哈哈哈，被重置有点上瘾了都</p></div>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17891763\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/14542d85008653367af4686fe65b8565?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"SD10\" data-uid=\"228983\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>28</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/SD10\">SD10</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-22 12:38:13 +08:00\">20h 1m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>昨天刚冲的，还抠抠嗖嗖地计划呢，结果一睁眼 100%了，后悔没有狠狠蹬</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17891970\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c6a7919632a1797e1f075dc31ffb0e87?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"sn0w